it wasn’t our first time traveling to amsterdam, but it was our first time flying @klm and they did not disappoint. we flew from YYZ to AMS direct in their new premium comfort class cabin which has way more space, wider seats with extra legroom and recline, and just more overall comfort than economy. don’t even get me started on how good the food was compared to other airlines I have flown. 

they served tuna sashimi... tuna sashimi on a flight?? what!! & it was bomb. all drinks – alcoholic and non alcoholic are also included during the flight. you HAVE to try their signature espresso martini as a little night cap. It was so good – kris mixed it with her vanilla ice cream to make a little affogato. mmmm…  this was definitely the best way to fly at a WAY more affordable price than business class. 

im already wishing we could do the entire trip over again. best city, 10/10 flight experience :)

#KLMpartner #PremiumComfort #klm

📍seitan limania beach : a total must visit if you’re visiting chania, crete!! 🇬🇷 

this was one of the coolest most unique beaches we have ever been to!! it was absolutely stunning. a small remote beach tucked away in a cove surrounded by epic rocky cliffs. bring runners for the walk down and the drive to the beach was a tad sketchy (lol) with the classic cretan narrow windy no railing roads but totally worth it. it had beauty crystal clear turquoise waters and even some friendly mountain goats. they are not shy at all and will dabble right into your bag if they think you have food 😂 it was a perfect way to spend our first afternoon in chania. 

swipe to see kris join the cliff jumpers .. way too high 😂🫣 i sent the video to my mom and all she said was “i hope you guys have health insurance” haha 

12/10 highlight of the trip 🤘🏻
